snippet.title: Purrs in Heaven - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description: Purrs in Heaven will come to Nintendo Switch on April 17, 2020. Poor Lanna gone to heaven after a tragic accident. Luckily, she has a chance to come back to life. Help the kitten to pass all trials and defeat the guardians who guard the 3 pieces of her soul in this platform-puzzle game. Do you accept the challenge?
